<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="ff18Dec1937"><font color="red">18 December 1937</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to T.S. Eliot): My covering letter got lost &hellip; I am sending you with this letter the 1st portion of Section III to be followed in a week or so by the 2nd and final portion. Section IV will follow in due course. </div>
